<div class="title">Great Study Helper!</div>
<div class="substance">Caffeine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Mcbain&Exact=1">Mcbain</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Mcbain. "Great Study Helper!: An Experience with Caffeine (exp6650)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 22, 2002. erowid.org/exp/6650</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
